---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

const timelineImgs = Object.values(
  import.meta.glob<ImageMetadata>("@/assets/images/about/timeline/*", {
    eager: true,
    import: "default",
  }),
);
---

<section
  id="timeline"
  aria-labelledby="timeline-heading"
  class="mx-auto w-full max-w-(--breakpoint-2xl) overflow-hidden px-4"
>
  <h2 id="timeline-heading" class="mb-12 text-2xl font-bold">
    혁신적인 금융시장을 향한 여정
  </h2>
  <ol
    class="before:bg-primary relative grid before:absolute before:h-full before:w-1 before:rounded-full lg:grid-cols-7 lg:before:h-0.5 lg:before:w-[calc(100%+1rem)] lg:before:justify-self-center lg:before:[grid-area:3/1/3/-1]"
  >
    <li
      class="max-lg:border-primary grid max-lg:border-b-2 max-lg:py-4 max-lg:ps-4 lg:row-span-3 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
    >
      <div
        class="before:bg-primary relative grid before:absolute before:start-[1px] before:bottom-[-1px] before:size-2 before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-1/2 before:rounded-full max-lg:before:hidden lg:row-span-2 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
      >
        <time class="text-base-content/75" datetime="2021-01">2021년 1분기</time
        >
        <p class="lg:border-primary mt-4 lg:border-s-2 lg:px-2 lg:pb-2">
          말레이시아 전 총리 마하티르 모하마드는 대한민국 전 국무총리 한승수와
          그의 회사 GG56을 라부안으로 초청하여, 라부안을 글로벌 금융 허브로
          재활성화하기 위한 협력을 제안
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-lg:mt-4 lg:p-2">
        <Image src={timelineImgs[0]} alt="" class="rounded-box shadow-sm" />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li
      class="max-lg:border-primary grid max-lg:border-b-2 max-lg:py-4 max-lg:ps-4 lg:row-span-3 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
    >
      <div
        class="before:bg-primary relative grid before:absolute before:start-[1px] before:bottom-[-1px] before:size-2 before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-1/2 before:rounded-full max-lg:before:hidden lg:row-span-2 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
      >
        <time class="text-base-content/75" datetime="2022-01">2022년 1분기</time
        >
        <p class="lg:border-primary mt-4 lg:border-s-2 lg:px-2 lg:pb-2">
          <strong>GG56 Labuan 법인 설립 (납입자본금 미화 100만 달러)</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-lg:mt-4 lg:p-2">
        <Image src={timelineImgs[4]} alt="" class="rounded-box shadow-sm" />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li
      class="max-lg:border-primary grid max-lg:border-b-2 max-lg:py-4 max-lg:ps-4 lg:row-span-3 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
    >
      <div
        class="before:bg-primary relative grid before:absolute before:start-[1px] before:bottom-[-1px] before:size-2 before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-1/2 before:rounded-full max-lg:before:hidden lg:row-span-2 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
      >
        <time class="text-base-content/75" datetime="2023-01">2023년 1분기</time
        >
        <p class="lg:border-primary mt-4 lg:border-s-2 lg:px-2 lg:pb-2">
          <strong>GGEX Korea 법인 설립</strong><br />
          한국 내 암호화폐 거래소 사업에서 ‘글로벌’ 거래소로 피벗 전환 국내 16개
          거래소에 대한 실사 수행
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-lg:mt-4 lg:p-2">
        <Image src={timelineImgs[1]} alt="" class="rounded-box shadow-sm" />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li
      class="max-lg:border-primary grid max-lg:border-b-2 max-lg:py-4 max-lg:ps-4 lg:row-span-3 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
    >
      <div
        class="before:bg-primary relative grid before:absolute before:start-[1px] before:bottom-[-1px] before:size-2 before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-1/2 before:rounded-full max-lg:before:hidden lg:row-span-2 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
      >
        <time class="text-base-content/75" datetime="2024-01">2024년 1분기</time
        >
        <p class="lg:border-primary mt-4 lg:border-s-2 lg:px-2 lg:pb-2">
          말레이시아 안와르 이브라힘 총리와 합의하여, <strong
            >말레이시아 스마트시티 자금조달 및 라부안의 혁신적 디지털 금융
            도입을 위해 GG56과 파트너십 합의</strong
          >
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-lg:mt-4 lg:p-2">
        <Image src={timelineImgs[2]} alt="" class="rounded-box shadow-sm" />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li
      class="max-lg:border-primary grid max-lg:border-b-2 max-lg:py-4 max-lg:ps-4 lg:row-span-3 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
    >
      <div
        class="before:bg-primary relative grid before:absolute before:start-[1px] before:bottom-[-1px] before:size-2 before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-1/2 before:rounded-full max-lg:before:hidden lg:row-span-2 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
      >
        <time class="text-base-content/75" datetime="2024-07">2024년 3분기</time
        >
        <p class="lg:border-primary mt-4 lg:border-s-2 lg:px-2 lg:pb-2">
          <strong
            >이브라힘 이스칸다르 국왕실과 GG56은 라부안내 혁신 디지털 금융 도입</strong
          >과 말레이시아 포레스트 시티의 자금조달 및 개발 가속화를 위한 <strong
            >MOA를 체결</strong
          >
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-lg:mt-4 lg:p-2">
        <Image src={timelineImgs[3]} alt="" class="rounded-box shadow-sm" />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li
      class="max-lg:border-primary grid max-lg:border-b-2 max-lg:py-4 max-lg:ps-4 lg:row-span-3 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
    >
      <div
        class="before:bg-primary relative grid before:absolute before:start-[1px] before:bottom-[-1px] before:size-2 before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-1/2 before:rounded-full max-lg:before:hidden lg:row-span-2 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
      >
        <time class="text-base-content/75" datetime="2025-04">2025년 2분기</time
        >
        <p class="lg:border-primary mt-4 lg:border-s-2 lg:px-2 lg:pb-2">
          GGEX 코어 시스템 완료(2024년 4분기) 및 <strong
            >상업 운영 개시(2025년 2분기)</strong
          >
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-lg:mt-4 lg:p-2">
        <Image src={timelineImgs[5]} alt="" class="rounded-box shadow-sm" />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="grid max-lg:py-4 max-lg:ps-4 lg:row-span-3 lg:grid-rows-subgrid">
      <div
        class="before:bg-primary relative grid before:absolute before:start-[1px] before:bottom-[-1px] before:size-2 before:-translate-x-1/2 before:translate-y-1/2 before:rounded-full max-lg:before:hidden lg:row-span-2 lg:grid-rows-subgrid"
      >
        <time class="text-base-content/75" datetime="2025-01/2026-01"
          >2025년 1분기 ~ 2026년 1분기</time
        >
        <p class="lg:border-primary mt-4 lg:border-s-2 lg:px-2 lg:pb-2">
          <strong
            >GGBank 인가 취득(2026년 1분기) 및 단일 플랫폼을 통한 GGBank & GGEX
            통합 서비스 운영 개시<br />(2026년 4분기)</strong
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</section>
